---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="SocialProof Documentation — Guides and Help"
  description="Everything you need to get started with SocialProof. Collect testimonials, embed widgets, and turn customer reviews into revenue."
  canonical="https://socialproof.dev/docs"
>
<style>
  .docs-hero { padding: 60px 24px 40px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .docs-hero h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .docs-hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #555; }
  .docs-grid { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px 80px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; }
  .doc-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: box-shadow 0.15s; display: block; }
  .doc-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border-color: #6c47ff; }
  .doc-card .emoji { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }
  .doc-card h2 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .doc-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
  .help-strip { background: #f5f3ff; text-align: center; padding: 40px 24px; }
  .help-strip p { color: #555; margin: 0; }
  .help-strip a { color: #6c47ff; font-weight: 600; }
</style>

<div class="docs-hero">
  <h1>Documentation</h1>
  <p>Everything you need to collect, approve, and display customer testimonials.</p>
</div>

<div class="docs-grid">
  <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="doc-card">
    <span class="emoji">🚀</span>
    <h2>Quick Start</h2>
    <p>Get your first testimonial in under 5 minutes. No widget setup required to get started.</p>
  </a>
  <a href="/docs/collecting" class="doc-card">
    <span class="emoji">📬</span>
    <h2>Collecting Testimonials</h2>
    <p>Email requests, collection links, QR codes — every way to ask happy customers for a review.</p>
  </a>
  <a href="/docs/embedding" class="doc-card">
    <span class="emoji">🔧</span>
    <h2>Embedding Your Widget</h2>
    <p>Add a testimonial carousel, grid, or badge to any website with one line of code.</p>
  </a>
</div>

<div class="help-strip">
  <p>Can't find what you need? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@socialproof.dev">hello@socialproof.dev</a> — we respond within one business day.</p>
</div>
</Base>
